### ============================================================================
### Screenshot Capture Service — Tests
### ============================================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@apiKey = dev-api-key


### Capture a screenshot from a website
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/captures
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "url": "https://github.com",
  "entity_type": "application",
  "entity_id": "github-home",
  "options": {
    "viewports": ["card"],
    "wait_strategy": "domcontentloaded",
    "delay_after_load_ms": 3000
  }
}

###

### Check result (replace the job_id)
@jobId = REPLACE_WITH_JOB_ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/captures/{{jobId}}
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
